gh Cowan]]\n| 1867\n| 1943\n| historian\n| ''Ontario and the Detroit Frontier 1701\u20131814''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[James Alexander Cowan]]\n| 1901\n| 1978\n| writer, columnist\n| \n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Daniel Allen Cox]]\n| 1976\n|\n| novelist\n| ''Shuck'', ''Tattoo This Madness In''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Ivan Coyote]]\n| 1969\n|\n| spoken-word poet, columnist\n| ''Bow Grip''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Archie Crail]]\n| 1944\n|\n| playwright, short stories\n| ''Exile'', ''The Bonus Deal''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Isabella Valancy Crawford]]\n| 1846\n| 1887\n| poet, freelance\n| ''Old Spookses' Pass''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Donald Creighton]]\n| 1902\n| 1979\n| historian\n| ''John A. Macdonald''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Luella Creighton]]\n| 1901\n| 1996\n| historical fiction, children's non-fiction\n| ''High Bright Buggy Wheels''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Octave Cr\u00e9mazie]]\n| 1827\n| 1879\n| poet\n| \n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Eva Crocker]]\n| \n| \n| short stories\n| ''Barrelling Forward''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Lynn Crosbie]]\n| 1963\n|\n| poet, novelist\n| ''Life Is About Losing Everything''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Lorna Crozier]]\n| 1948\n|\n| poet\n| ''Inventing the Hawk'', ''Everything Arrives at the Light''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Michael Crummey]]\n| 1965\n|\n| poet, novelist, non-fiction\n| ''[[Galore (novel)|Galore]], Sweetland, Hard Light, River Thieves, The Innocents''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Nancy Jo Cullen]]\n| \n|\n| poet, short stories\n| ''Science Fiction Saint'', ''Pearl'', ''Untitled Child'', ''Canary''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Alan Cumyn]]\n| 1960\n|\n| novelist\n| ''The Secret Life of Owen Skye'', ''Dear Sylvia''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Peter Cureton]]\n| 1965\n| 1994\n| playwright\n| ''Passages''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Andrea Curtis]]\n| \n|\n| creative non-fiction\n| ''[[Into the Blue (book)|Into the Blue]]''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Herb Curtis]]\n| 1949\n|\n| novelist, humorist\n| ''The Last Tasmanian'', ''Luther Corhern