anc]]\n| 1980\n|\n| novelist\n| ''L'homme blanc'', ''Malabourg''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[D. M. LeBourdais]]\n| 1887\n| 1964\n| journalist, historian\n| ''Nation of the North: Canada Since Confederation'', ''Canada and the Atomic Revolution''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Isabel LeBourdais]]\n| 1909\n| 2003\n| journalist\n| ''[[The Trial of Steven Truscott]]''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[F\u00e9lix Leclerc]]\n| 1914\n| 1988\n| writer, poet, singer-songwriter\n| ''Pieds nus dans l'aube'', ''Le calepin d'un fl\u00e2neur'', ''Moi, mes souliers''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Dennis Lee (author)|Dennis Lee]]\n| 1939\n| \n| poet\n| ''Garbage Delight'', ''Alligator Pie'', ''Civil Elegies''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[John Alan Lee]]\n| 1933\n| 2013\n| sociologist\n| ''The Colours of Love'', ''Getting Sex''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[JJ Lee (writer)|JJ Lee]]\n| \n|\n| non-fiction\n| ''The Measure of a Man: The Story of a Father, a Son, and a Suit''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Jen Sookfong Lee]]\n|\n| \n| novelist\n| ''The End of East''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[John B. Lee]]\n| 1951\n|\n| poet\n| ''The Pig Dance Dreams'', ''Variations on Herb''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Nancy Lee (writer)|Nancy Lee]]\n| 1970\n|\n| short stories\n| ''Dead Girls''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Ronald Lee]]\n| 1934\n|\n| novelist\n| ''Goddam Gypsy''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Sky Lee]]\n| 1952\n| \n| short stories, novelist\n| ''Disappearing Moon Cafe''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Mathyas Lefebure]]\n| \n|\n| novelist\n| ''D'o\u00f9 viens tu, berger?''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Lily Alice Lefevre]]\n| 1854\n| 1938\n| poet\n| ''The Lions' Gate and Other Verses'', ''A Garden By The Sea''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Mark Leiren-Young]]\n| 1962\n|\n| playwright, novelist\n| ''[[Shylock (play)]]'', ''The Killer Whale Who Changed the World'', ''Never Shoot A Stampede Queen'' \n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Roger Lemelin]]\n| 1919\n| 1992\n| novelist, essayist\n| ''The Town Below''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Matt Lennox]]\n| 1980\n|\n| novelis