atawabin]]\n| \n|\n| memoirist\n| ''Up Ghost River: A Chief\u2019s Journey Through the Turbulent Waters of Native History''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[John Metcalf (writer)|John Metcalf]]\n| 1938\n|\n| \n| \n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Sarah Mian]]\n|\n| \n| poet, novelist, short stories\n| ''When the Saints''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Anne Michaels]]\n| 1958\n| \n| poet, novelist\n| ''[[Fugitive Pieces]]''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Sean Michaels (writer)|Sean Michaels]]\n| 1982\n|\n| novelist, music critic\n| ''[[Us Conductors]]''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Andr\u00e9e A. Michaud]]\n| 1957\n|\n| novelist, playwright\n| ''Le ravissement'', ''Mirror Lake'', ''Bondr\u00e9e''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Marianne Micros]]\n| \n| \n| short stories, poetry\n| ''Eye''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Stevie Mikayne]]\n|\n| \n| mystery novelist, children's literature\n| ''UnCatholic Conduct'', ''Illicit Artifacts''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Roy Miki]]\n| 1942\n| \n| \n| \n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Ron Miksha]]\n| 1954\n|\n| \n| ''Bad Beekeeping''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Eleanor Millard]]\n| 1942\n|\n| novelist, memoirist, short stories\n| ''River Child'', ''Journeys Outside and In'', ''Summer Snow''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[John Miller (writer)|John Miller]]\n| 1968\n|\n| novelist\n| ''The Featherbed'', ''A Sharp Intake of Breath''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Orlo Miller]]\n| 1911\n| 1993\n| historian, novelist\n| \n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Kenneth G. Mills]]\n| 1923\n| 2004\n| poet\n| \n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Christine Miscione]]\n| \n|\n| novelist, short stories\n| ''Auxiliary Skins'', ''Carafola''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Christian Mistral]]\n| 1964\n|\n| novelist, poet, songwriter\n| ''Vamp''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Rohinton Mistry]]\n| 1952\n|\n| novelist\n| ''[[Such a Long Journey (novel)|Such a Long Journey]]'', ''[[A Fine Balance]]''\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[Jared Mitchell (writer)|Jared Mitchell]]\n| 1955\n| \n| \n| \n|-\n| scope=\"row\" | [[W.O. Mitchell]]\n| 1914\n| 1998\n| novelist, sho